<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Activation de compte - Mwinda Technologies</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f6f9fc;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #001F3F;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .logo-title {
            color: #001F3F;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .logo-subtitle {
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .content h1 {
            color: #001F3F;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            color: #4a5568;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .activation-link {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #001F3F 0%, #0056b3 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 15px 35px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 31, 63, 0.2);
        }

        .info-box {
            margin: 30px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .warning-box {
            margin: 40px 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #001F3F;
            border-radius: 8px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        .footer-title {
            color: #001F3F;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .footer-text {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- En-tête avec logo -->
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <div class="logo-title">
                    MWINDA
                    <div class="logo-subtitle">TECHNOLOGIES</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Contenu principal -->
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Activation de votre compte</h1>
            <p>Bonjour,<br><br>Pour activer votre compte chez Mwinda Technologies, cliquez sur le lien ci-dessous :</p>

            <!-- Lien d'activation -->
            <a href="https://mwinda.core-techs.ca/identity/activate-email-step3/{{email}}" class="activation-link">Activer mon compte</a>

            <!-- Identifiant -->
            <div class="info-box">
                <p>Email associé : <strong style="color: #001F3F;">{{email}}</strong></p>
            </div>

            <!-- Avertissement -->
            <div class="warning-box">
                <p>
                    <strong style="color: #001F3F;">Important :</strong><br>
                    • Ce lien d'activation est valable pendant 24 heures<br>
                    • Si vous n'avez pas créé de compte, veuillez ignorer cet email
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <div class="footer-title">Mwinda Technologies</div>
            <div class="footer-text">Illuminer l'avenir par l'innovation</div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
